The proof needs to be adjusted in the `case cons C σ` part, specifically within the `case Caller` branch of the `cases ra : roleOfIn a C` statement.

The goal at the `sorry` location is:
`⊢ (b, @S b) ∈ Error.resultSet n a S ⟨σ, Error.resultSet._proof_2 n σ a c o⟩ ∨ (b, @S b) ∈ Error.resultSet n c S ⟨σ, Error.resultSet._proof_2 n σ a c o⟩`

